{"tid":903660,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候要教下你班仆街搭巴士","createTime":"2018-11-15T17:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T16:36:14.000Z","uid":26418,"like":121,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e913c2ed6637ac9a4eef28a4573e94c44586e6f5","tid":903660,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"小弟做左巴士乘客廿幾年<br />\n眼見依加巴士乘客質素每況愈下<br />\n所以就專登出POST教下你班仆街搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 預早時間出門口/出門口前先睇交通消息</strong></span><br />\n呢句老生常談 交通情況冇得預計<br />\n雖然好多人都屌九巴APP到站時間預報要改善<br />\n但其實好多時 有d突發情況冇計既....<br />\n例如：<br />\ni) 大家都知沙田市中心出面一大堆死車 好多時都搞到巴士總站塞車<br />\n咁樣搞一搞 又要等燈 自然APP上面寫既2分鐘就唔準啦<br />\nii) 沙田市中心間唔中會有訓練巴士 大家都知訓練巴士開好慢<br />\n自然會令到後面D巴士跟住慢啦 咁仲點會係APP上面寫既3分鐘呢？<br />\niii) 巴士有時會壞車/司機會突然間唔舒服 班次突然間開唔到 <br />\n咁APP後面個資料庫又點會更新得切呢？<br />\niv) 前一個站冇客 架車又開得快 過到綠燈 咁班次咪會早左兩分鐘到達....<br />\n太多情況不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只希望大家唔好好似d廢老咁 <br />\n送車尾/等左好耐先有車/冇左班車 喺到屌司機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2. 攞定八達通出黎</strong></span><br />\n呢個唔洗多講啦 上到車先搵八達通/磨袋<br />\n阻撚住全車人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>3. 架車埋站前 揮揮手</strong></span><br />\n大佬呀 好多巴士站 閒閒地都幾條線<br />\n係咪每架車經過都要埋站 停車 開門啊?<br />\n要上車 揮個手有幾難?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>4. 請緊握扶手</strong></span><br />\n九巴每次報完站 後面都會加句「請緊握扶手」<br />\n但眼見每日有唔少人 又冇能力唔扶手又企得穩<br />\n特別係坐樓上 又要喺架車開緊既時候行落去下層既人<br />\n陣間前面有DC9急剎車(唔係針對DC9 只係做例子) <br />\n你成個人飛左去車頭撞爆部電視就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">5. 攞住大型行李/湊住細路/老人家 唔好坐上層</span></strong><br />\n咁辛苦自己何必呢？陣間個細路捉唔到扶手/老人家企唔穩....<br />\n另外親眼見過一單....有條仆街攞行李上車(本身太大係唔上得車，但司機隻眼開隻眼閉)<br />\n行李就放輪椅位 個人就坐上層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住架車一開 個行李周圍碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n司機即刻停車 上去上層屌柒個乘客<br />\n陣間撞親人/撞爆對門 係咪你負責先？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>6. 切勿飲食/剪指甲/大聲傾計(傾電話)/唔戴耳筒睇片</strong></span><br />\n朝早趕時間 咬個包/飲盒野 點會有人理你?<br />\n但你走去食燒味飯/倒瀉野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外近排愈黎愈多廢老大聲播片/播歌 聽過多數都係普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傾計/講電話大聲都有唔少<br />\n尊重自己 尊重他人 好難咩？<br />\n(雖然九巴啲車好污糟 好似冇人清潔咁 例如車窗D頭油/窗台D塵<br />\n但其實有好多位都係人為造成 例如紙巾/香口膠/膠樽<br />\n少左呢啲人為垃圾 架車點都乾淨啲啦)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">7. 落車前 記得禁鐘</span></strong><br />\n唔好以為下個站係轉車站/大站 一定要開門俾你落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9329e7cf58774e69d0e4a6bf7b638ac7939735","tid":903660,"uid":211567,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"仲有頂椅背嗰班廢中廢老<br />\n頂都算 仲要頂下又唔頂先仆街"},{"pid":"6a33e6d03ceb0c92bef105847b98bfccf17dc1c9","tid":903660,"uid":26418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a9329e7cf58774e69d0e4a6bf7b638ac7939735","tid":903660,"uid":211567,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"仲有頂椅背嗰班廢中廢老<br />\n頂都算 仲要頂下又唔頂先仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  腳唔撚夠伸就坐下層/上層走廊位啦"},{"pid":"bc17b366e93ea003df8cdcc1f457c1b7f043b2bd","tid":903660,"uid":180371,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"記得入少兩毫紙要講唔好意思！"},{"pid":"b1a559e957b180bf75195f8c0fd8fb2188ca5e79","tid":903660,"uid":55830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好伸腳出走廊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9740eb7b02b3a1882f83e775be933aa00501bc77","tid":903660,"uid":51593,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"個袋坐個位 跟住人坐出面 嗰啲仆街真係要大大力屌落去"},{"pid":"6d29f79d9472223a3f77731ef53b8d9d99d65fc3","tid":903660,"uid":29387,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"請儘量行入車尾啦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆班</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031bbb94b027634b672316abcc130d3ce7c58b61","tid":903660,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人係背到大部份巴士路線number係邊到去邊到"},{"pid":"fca0b334d290fd69b078409b074640280a067a2b","tid":903660,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498fb9a435d41b0ef92187f4c7fc3e7dfb2d9d19","tid":903660,"uid":100760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"031bbb94b027634b672316abcc130d3ce7c58b61","tid":903660,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人係背到大部份巴士路線number係邊到去邊到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:26:43.000Z","msg":"咁都要問，實有巴膠背到啦"},{"pid":"8014eef5738c8ff6987054d5d5bba6e97f906c78","tid":903660,"uid":100760,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"樓主講嘅正常人都會識，無奈個世界就係有好多唔撚正常嘅人"},{"pid":"91fd9b626d232ebb75981c89f67513327d2a1256","tid":903660,"uid":196099,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T18:29:04.000Z","msg":"咪撚ar開隻腳坐"},{"pid":"d13b9805e765c35c43fb28be24c87a207bc23d1a","tid":903660,"uid":63132,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:13:18.000Z","msg":"擺咗行李起傷殘位，唔好上樓上係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本個傷殘又唔係預你擺野，<br />\n有輪椅上都要比人地優先用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次見到有一家三口，<br />\n擺架bb車過去，跟住想上樓上坐，<br />\n個司機就話最好坐返樓下，<br />\n如果有輪椅上嚟可以讓返比人，<br />\n個女人就發晒癲: 依家啲司機咁無禮貌，同人講野唔講唔該㗎？！<br />\n心諗，你錯先喎，霸咗個位又走咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af73b4e890160f86b912ed08c8d4c3a450d3e0b","tid":903660,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:26:39.000Z","msg":"開係度做乜姐，上得嚟個個都後生仔比較好教養，更係開係facebook 廢老group 啦"},{"pid":"c59ca12c1599f5aa6d74786dca869381f88df4e7","tid":903660,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"031bbb94b027634b672316abcc130d3ce7c58b61","tid":903660,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人係背到大部份巴士路線number係邊到去邊到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:32:58.000Z","msg":"大嶼山以外都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道個pattern就知大約去邊<br />\n3字頭係人都知係去荃葵<br />\n31系去石籬 36系去梨木樹<br />\n58系去良景 59系屯碼 60系去市中心"},{"pid":"fe184e6de6efb1876736e604f57f2a51a19dc362","tid":903660,"uid":190253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:33:33.000Z","msg":"停好車先叫人唔該借借啦，轉緊個大彎居然叫我鬆開個扶手借開俾啲廢老行去車門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"7ae3fcd9023a159715811416d7b47d53d4cd153d","tid":903660,"uid":150775,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"c59ca12c1599f5aa6d74786dca869381f88df4e7","tid":903660,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"031bbb94b027634b672316abcc130d3ce7c58b61","tid":903660,"uid":203619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:21:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人係背到大部份巴士路線number係邊到