br />\n58系去良景 59系屯碼 60系去市中心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T19:56:07.000Z","msg":"系你老母閪咩屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T20:05:33.000Z","msg":"系列個系呀<br />\n唔好係唔係都系人老母啦"},{"pid":"c718872668d2912b18b15f8e70fd4cb8c2aff773","tid":903660,"uid":37259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T20:43:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩搭完 N 車見到可以講下<br />\n坐對頭位咪撚飛象過河伸腳去對面位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f82b38254036ebbe199b9f1b21e91621062560","tid":903660,"uid":199252,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T21:10:04.000Z","msg":"落樓梯嗰陣行出d,唔好阻住後面同樣要落ge人，盡量有得企平地就企，企樓梯可以好危險"},{"pid":"63e5ed017bc350cd639f006def63e99890d67cec","tid":903660,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T21:39:46.000Z","msg":"係到教？ 會唔會有d好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd416aa4b65d21e69bf2ca268e5dadf5fd8bb89a","tid":903660,"uid":178459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T21:53:42.000Z","msg":"個啲大聲播片講電話真心請你去死 拜託<br />\n做人自私得太撚緊要<br />\n無須多講/解釋<br />\n體驗過就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成程車超不爽"},{"pid":"528610cdeaa65fdff5a4c64c3eb0df0b14e05487","tid":903660,"uid":26418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"63e5ed017bc350cd639f006def63e99890d67cec","tid":903660,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T21:39:46.000Z","msg":"係到教？ 會唔會有d好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:23:50.000Z","msg":"靠各位巴絲宣傳俾啲廢老知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有唔少00後搭巴士都喺到食野/大聲傾計<br />\n都希望佢地會睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655cb66435d934ae952ca689dc58c69abb5a304f","tid":903660,"uid":143849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d29f79d9472223a3f77731ef53b8d9d99d65fc3","tid":903660,"uid":29387,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"請儘量行入車尾啦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仆班</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"呢個係重點 成日係青沙站上唔到車 因為啲人唔行入啲"}]}